    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This issue happened to me while upgrading to Java 17, I solved it by configuring the new SDK in project structure and invalidate the caches : File --&gt; invalidate caches --&gt; default selection and restart.</p>\n"
