    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 39,
    "last_activity_date" : 1640792292,
    "creation_date" : 1640792292,
    "answer_id" : 70521631,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had the same problem. What helped in my case is the following. In IntelliJ IDEA I opened <code>File -&gt; Project structure</code> and then clicked <code>Modules</code> and changed the <code>Language level</code> to 17. Then I was able to run my code without problems.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/XEvmd.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/XEvmd.png\" alt=\"Project structure window\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
