  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 21429973,
      "reputation" : 21,
      "user_id" : 15786601,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14GhXaIJBvbVLP03RfNdQS1EifAHHFElPOwTzJPYhyw=k-s256",
      "display_name" : "Daniel McEnnis",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/15786601/daniel-mcennis"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1645035401,
    "last_edit_date" : 1645035401,
    "creation_date" : 1645035068,
    "answer_id" : 71147170,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Your error is likely from IntelliJ attempting to call a Java 17 parser for compliance with Java 17 syntax (regardless of the SDK type) and there is no Java 17 JDK installed to perform the syntax checking with. You have 2 options.</p>\n<p>Change 'Language Level' (Project Settings / Project in the Module Settings available from context window - right click - in the project window) to match your current SDK (ignoring possible language conflicts with more recent versions)</p>\n<p>Download a Java 17 JDK to perform parsing with. That is in Platform Settings/SDKs in the same context menu, select '+', select 'Download JDK', then download and install a Java 17 version.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 1801353,
        "reputation" : 83119,
        "user_id" : 1639625,
        "user_type" : "registered",
        "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/4224d1458a149d37b56a53115656f4df?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
        "display_name" : "tobias_k",
        "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1639625/tobias-k"
      },
      "edited" : false,
      "score" : 2,
      "creation_date" : 1699608786,
      "post_id" : 71180761,
      "comment_id" : 136556217,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "For me, Step (2) was missing, thanks!"
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 467725,
      "reputation" : 20887,
      "user_id" : 873282,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 55,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/1e6ae94f84a34641ccc5abc86a664694?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "koppor",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/873282/koppor"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 20,
    "last_activity_date" : 1645225313,
    "last_edit_date" : 1645225313,
    "creation_date" : 1645224904,
    "answer_id" : 71180761,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<ol>\n<li><p>Check that a JDK 17 is available at File -&gt; Project Structure -&gt; Platform Settings -&gt; &quot;SDKS&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/SzGhV.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/SzGhV.png\" alt=\"File -&gt; Project Structure -&gt; Platform Settings -&gt; &quot;SDKS&quot;\" /></a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Select the 17 JDK at File -&gt; Project Structure -&gt; Project Settings -&gt; &quot;Project&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/De3uC.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/De3uC.png\" alt=\"File -&gt; Project Structure -&gt; Project Settings -&gt; &quot;Project&quot;\" /></a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>File -&gt; Invalidate Caches... -&gt; (leave defaults) -&gt; &quot;Invalidate and Restart&quot;</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Do &quot;Build&quot; -&gt; &quot;Rebuild Project&quot;</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 19552439,
      "reputation" : 31,
      "user_id" : 14307693,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f822fceca6c64fcc655634902f8c761c?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "twu",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/14307693/twu"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1650653420,
    "last_edit_date" : 1650653420,
    "creation_date" : 1650397535,
    "answer_id" : 71930489,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For me these had to match...</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>File | Project Structure | Project | Project SDK</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>File | Project Structure | Modules | Language level</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>IntelliJ Idea | Preferences | Build, Exec... | Build Tools | Maven | Importing | JDK for importer</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>system.properties (file) java.runtime.version=</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>pom.xml - &lt;java.version&gt;</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n"
  }, {
