    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This worked for me. I went to Project Settings, clicked on Build, Execution, and Deployment, clicked on Java, clicked on Java Compiler, then changed the Java version (Target bytecode version) to 11.</p>\n"
