    "last_activity_date" : 1679833876,
    "creation_date" : 1679833876,
    "answer_id" : 75847758,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>There are two actions to take:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <code>File</code> -&gt; <code>Project structure</code> -&gt; <code>Modules</code> and changed the Language level to 17</li>\n<li>Go to <code>IntelliJ IDEA</code> -&gt; <code>Settings</code> -&gt; <code>Build, Execution, Deployment</code> -&gt; <code>Compiler</code> -&gt; <code>Java Compiler</code>. Change your module's <code>Target bytecode version version</code> to 17.</li>\n</ol>\n"
  }, {
