    "answer_id" : 76327888,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The solution that worked for me was to download Java version 17. You can do this by navigating to File - Project Structure - SDKs and clicking the + button under the Classpath <a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/u5ikD.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Download button</a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 11834138,
      "reputation" : 331,
      "user_id" : 8659981,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/4b21aaefbfbb6ad88013fdb11adb0964?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Jack Vicky",
