    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1691904368,
    "creation_date" : 1691904368,
    "answer_id" : 76892032,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have tried all the steps like changing the &quot;Target bytecode version&quot; and &quot;Project bytecode version&quot; and &quot;project language level&quot; but none got worked out. finally I fixed it by upgrading the JDK version from 1.8 to the latest version jdk-20.</p>\n<p>Note: Don't forget to change the JAVA_HOME path post upgrading the JDK :)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/gCKdR.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/gCKdR.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3673566,
      "reputation" : 2732,
      "user_id" : 3060133,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 92,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0db2a8cd45527c25255d4e0451923f9b?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Shirish Bari",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3060133/shirish-bari"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1699027524,
    "creation_date" : 1699027524,
    "answer_id" : 77418145,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I setup the SDK and Compiler version correctly still I had the same issue.</p>\n<p>Finally, after changing the gradle jvm to use java-17, issue got resolved.</p>\n<p>I followed below steps :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Press Ctrl+Alt+S(letter S) to open settings</li>\n<li>Go to Build, Execution and Deployment</li>\n<li>Then go to Build tool</li>\n<li>select gradle</li>\n<li>Change the gradle-jvm to java-17</li>\n</ul>\n<p>please refer below image:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/XOCAN.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/XOCAN.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
