    "last_activity_date" : 1702684457,
    "creation_date" : 1702684457,
    "answer_id" : 77669333,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For those using maven-compiler-plugin, adding version in plugin config solves the problem</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>    &lt;build&gt;\n        &lt;plugins&gt;\n            &lt;plugin&gt;\n                &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n                &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-compiler-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n                &lt;version&gt;3.11.0&lt;/version&gt;\n                &lt;configuration&gt;\n                    &lt;source&gt;17&lt;/source&gt;\n                    &lt;target&gt;17&lt;/target&gt;\n                &lt;/configuration&gt;\n            &lt;/plugin&gt;\n      ...\n     &lt;/build&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2803169,
      "reputation" : 383,
      "user_id" : 2410994,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 86,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/964537ce22e2abfcac98b7da84b4f662?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "alperc",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2410994/alperc"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1704791382,
    "creation_date" : 1704791382,
    "answer_id" : 77785541,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Upgrading from Java 8/11 to Java 17:</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n  &lt;maven.compiler.release&gt;17&lt;/maven.compiler.release&gt;\n  &lt;jdk.version&gt;1.17&lt;/jdk.version&gt;\n  ....\n</code></pre>\n   \n<pre><code>&lt;plugin&gt;\n   &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n   &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-compiler-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n   &lt;version&gt;3.11.0&lt;/version&gt;\n    &lt;configuration&gt;\n       &lt;source&gt;${jdk.version}&lt;/source&gt;\n       &lt;target&gt;${jdk.version}&lt;/target&gt;\n    &lt;/configuration&gt;\n&lt;/plugin&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
