    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here are the THREE locations I've seen:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/v810hdZo.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/v810hdZo.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/2QsxJ4M6.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/2QsxJ4M6.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/IYBCfZ5W.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/IYBCfZ5W.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/19zXhl73.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/19zXhl73.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
