    "last_activity_date" : 1732959397,
    "creation_date" : 1732959397,
    "answer_id" : 79239230,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case, the pom file is right, the java version, source, target version are set correctly, but I was compiling from command line and the default java interpreter is set to JAVA 1.8. Updating it to JAVA 17 made it work.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3489451,
      "reputation" : 1,
      "user_id" : 2919500,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/rGjo3.jpg?s=256",
