    "last_activity_date" : 1763582000,
    "creation_date" : 1763582000,
    "answer_id" : 79824872,
    "question_id" : 67098514,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As most of the answers indicate, the problem is the JRE/JDK version used for the build.\nIn my case, since i used Linux, i solved it with:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-bash prettyprint-override\"><code>sudo update-alternatives --config java\n</code></pre>\n<p>and selecting the correct version.</p>\n"
